reviewText: From my generation, purchased for my grandchildren, to pass on the fun... who doesn't love the Beverly Hillbillies!  The kids laughed just like we did. Suggest; Pass it on.

If you buy ANY item produced by Platinum, the theme song will be missing, especially from The Beverly Hillbillies, Petticoat Junction, and the Andy Griffith Show (and probably Green Acres). The theme music is replaced with some dumb replacement music.  It seems that if the theme song has words, Platinum will replace it with their own dumb music.  You have been warned!
